message: "If you use this paper, its data, or its reproduction scripts, please cite it as below."
preferred-citation:
  type: report
  title: "The Bithumb–Binance BTC-numéraire Premium: A Theoretical Framework with Calibrated Simulation Evidence on BNB Chain Tokens"
  authors:
    - family-names: "Kim"
      given-names: "HoKwang"
      name-particle: "김호광"
      affiliation: "Betalabs Inc."
      orcid: "https://orcid.org/0009-0002-0962-2175"
      email: "gameworker@gmail.com"
  abstract: >-
    This paper redefines the price discrepancy between the Korean exchange
    Bithumb and the global exchange Binance using a new measure of the kimchi
    premium expressed in BTC units, denoted π^BTC_X(t), accompanied by
    calibrated simulation evidence on daily series over 2020–2025. The
    BTC-numéraire premium is invariant to exchange-rate and stablecoin-level
    fluctuations by numerator–denominator cancellation (Proposition 1). A
    normalised variance ratio ρ_X controls for token-level own volatility,
    OLS regressions are reported with Newey–West HAC standard errors, and
    asymmetric volatility is estimated with an EGARCH(1,1) model using
    Student-t innovations. A cross-exchange comparison among Binance, OKX,
    Bybit and Bithumb identifies the kimchi premium as a regulatory cost
    rather than a market inefficiency, and KCS-detected illegal forex
    transactions of approximately 14.2 trillion KRW (2018–2025) and 2.04
    trillion KRW (2024–2025 partial) are reported as lower-bound indicators
    of the policy cost. Available in Korean, English, and Chinese editions.
  keywords:
    - "kimchi premium"
    - "BTC-numéraire"
    - "satoshi premium"
    - "BNB Chain"
    - "capital controls"
    - "triangular arbitrage"
    - "limits to arbitrage"
    - "EGARCH"
    - "Newey-West HAC"
    - "Bithumb"
    - "Binance"
    - "cryptocurrency regulation"
    - "Korean cryptocurrency market"
    - "Travel Rule"
    - "VAUPA"
    - "KoFIU"
  year: 2026
  month: 5
  date-published: "2026-05-13"
  version: "5.1"
  url: "https://github.com/gameworkerkim/vibe-investing/tree/main/Paper%20%EB%85%BC%EB%AC%B8"
