title: "The Bithumb–Binance BTC-numéraire Premium (Trilingual Edition)"
authors:
  - family-names: "Kim"
    given-names: "HoKwang"
    affiliation: "Betalabs Inc."
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0009-0002-0962-2175"
    email: "gameworker@gmail.com"
abstract: >-
  Theoretical framework and calibrated simulation evidence for a new
  BTC-numéraire measure of the kimchi premium, applied to BNB Chain tokens
  (BNB, Venus/XVS) and ETH baseline on Bithumb and Binance. Includes
  cross-exchange comparison with OKX and Bybit, and quantitative policy
  cost analysis using Korea Customs Service detection data. Available in
  Korean, English, and Chinese editions.
